1
00:00:03,201 --> 00:00:07,644
intervyu mitn Zheni Pinkesovitsh,

2
00:00:07,644 --> 00:00:10,991
dem tsveytn VIDEO FILM.

3
00:00:11,959 --> 00:00:16,251
ir zent geven a dray khadoshim in AUSCHWITZ,

4
00:00:16,251 --> 00:00:18,805
un me hot aykh geshikt tsu

5
00:00:19,013 --> 00:00:20,947
a ARBEITSLAGER.

6
00:00:20,194 --> 00:00:22,432
in an arbets-lager, yo.

7
00:00:23,367 --> 00:00:24,188
vu?

8
00:00:24,531 --> 00:00:27,236
in ⟨Gruben⟩. dort iz gevezn

9
00:00:27,236 --> 00:00:30,570
a fabrik fun MUNITION,

10
00:00:30,570 --> 00:00:32,946
fun azolekhe zakhn.

11
00:00:32,158 --> 00:00:37,940
GRÄBEN iz, G.R.A UMLAUT.B.E.N.,

12
00:00:38,115 --> 00:00:40,727
NEAR GROSS-ROSEN.

13
00:00:40,727 --> 00:00:45,020
G.R.O.S.S.-O.... R.O.S.E.N.

14
00:00:45,979 --> 00:00:47,745
vos hot ir getun dortn?

15
00:00:48,291 --> 00:00:52,370
