ze'mir gegangen, a gantse nakht ho'mir gearbet bay,

17
00:00:55,783 --> 00:00:58,868
 dort iz gevezn fun,

18
00:00:58,868 --> 00:01:04,270
 f- fli- f-, nu, f- aerodrom,... nisht aerodrom...

19
00:01:04,270 --> 00:01:07,000
fli-mashinen teyln.

20
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:12,720
fun farshidene MUNITIONEN iz gevezn dort teyln, un ver bay vos hot gearbet.

21
00:01:12,550 --> 00:01:14,103
m'hot gemakht gever?

22
00:01:13,850 --> 00:01:16,040
