45
00:03:05,873 --> 00:03:08,195
s'iz geven a ARBEITSLAGER?

46
00:03:05,890 --> 00:03:06,576
un...

47
00:03:07,780 --> 00:03:17,224
an arbets-lager, ober dos iz oykhet ar⟨UNK⟩ un arum farnumen gevezn. undz ho'mir oykh nisht gezen vu me firt undz, vos me firt undz.

48
00:03:17,348 --> 00:03:19,805
dort ze'mir geven a shtikl tsayt,

49
00:03:20,419 --> 00:03:23,940
un m'hot nisht gebroykht hobn aza sakh mentshn,

50
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:33,052
hot men undz gevolt tsetey-..., zey hobn nisht gevust. zey hobn dos, az tsvey hot geheysn blayb'mir, un tsvey geyen avek.

51
00:03:33,345 --> 00:03:39,350
un demolts ho'mir gezogt far, farn kapo, tsi far vemen, az

52
00:03:39,437 --> 00:03:44,083
undz ze'mir shvesters, ze'mir aroysgekumen funem, fun,

53
00:03:44,083 --> 00:03:50,310
UNK, nu, fun Oyshvits. "nu," zogt zi, "⟨ets zents⟩ aroysgekumen un ⟨ets vets⟩ geyn in eynem.

54
00:03:50,310 --> 00:03:52,053
m'vet enk nisht tseraysn.

55
00:03:52,144 --> 00:03:54,580
az ets hot⟨s⟩ shoyn durkhgelebt..."

56
