57
00:03:55,283 --> 00:03:58,030
a kapo tsi... ikh gedenk nisht BEDIYUK.

58
00:03:58,030 --> 00:04:03,565
"az ets hot⟨s⟩ shoyn durkhgelebt Oyshvits, un m'hot enk nisht farbrent, m'hot enk nisht tseteylt,

59
00:04:03,565 --> 00:04:07,760
vet ets geyn vayter in eynem." azoy vi ze'mir ale fir avek.

60
00:04:07,050 --> 00:04:09,958
yo. vi lang zent ir geven in GRÄBEN?

61
00:04:10,538 --> 00:04:12,641
 a por vokhn.

62
00:04:13,542 --> 00:04:14,616
por vokhn?

63
00:04:14,166 --> 00:04:17,805
yo, un dernokh ze'mir gevezn in BAD KUDOWA.

64
00:04:20,038 --> 00:04:22,140
BAR KUD⟨EBADEN⟩?

65
00:04:21,422 --> 00:04:23,137
BAD KUDOWA.

66
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:26,883
OKAY. B.A.D. K.U.D.O.V.A.

67
00:04:27,109 --> 00:04:30,258
vu iz dos? dos iz vayt fun GRÄBEN?

68
00:04:30,298 --> 00:04:37,902
undz hot men alts azoy gezen tsu firn, mir zol'mir nisht zen tsi s'iz vayt, tsi s'iz noent. m'hot undz arumgefirt, arumgefirt...

69
00:04:36,289 --> 00:04:38,865
vi zent ir gekumen dortn? ⟨in⟩ a ban?

70
00:04:38,871 --> 00:04:42,010
