71
00:04:41,689 --> 00:04:43,910
ir hot gefort a tog⟨, a⟩ tsvey?

72
00:04:44,912 --> 00:04:51,386
m'hot geflegt tsu firn iber nakht spetsyal, mir zol'mir nisht visn BEDIYUK vi- vifl dos iz.

73
00:04:51,662 --> 00:04:59,160
nu, un dort ho'mir oykhet gearbet. dort ho'mir shoyn shverer gearbet. dort iz shoyn oykh nisht geven zeyer gut.

74
00:04:59,205 --> 00:05:01,291
