76
00:05:04,859 --> 00:05:05,859
flaks?

77
00:05:05,450 --> 00:05:08,630
yo. nokh dem ho'mir gearbet

78
00:05:08,630 --> 00:05:10,220
in a tsuker-...

79
00:05:08,655 --> 00:05:10,235
