80
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:12,800
yo... in a tsuker-ribn fabrik.

81
00:05:12,587 --> 00:05:15,787
tsuker-f- fun, f- fun, fun burikes?

82
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:16,735
burikes.

83
00:05:16,735 --> 00:05:22,371
dort ho'mir undz... dos ho-, rusn, dort iz geven rusishe oykhet,

84
00:05:22,371 --> 00:05:24,051
nisht,... mener.

85
00:05:24,051 --> 00:05:30,190
zey hobn es ge- zey hobn dos bay nakht getriknt un tsamgeleygt in di zek,

86
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:34,353
un undz hot men, zey hot men avekgefirt, undz ze'mir gekumen,

87
00:05:34,353 --> 00:05:38,434
un undz ho'mir gebundn di zek un ge- geleygt tsam.

88
00:05:39,385 --> 00:05:45,403
in, in BAD KUDOVA, s'iz geven beser oder erger fun GRÄBEN, oder di zelbe zakh?

89
00:05:44,835 --> 00:05:47,076
 s'iz arger gevezn.

90
00:05:47,076 --> 00:05:49,560
dort iz shoyn nisht geven oykh azoy gut.

91
00:05:49,712 --> 00:05:53,160
dort ho'mir shoyn ⟨z-⟩ i shver gearbet,

92
00:05:54,083 --> 00:05:56,625
esn iz nisht gevezn azoy,

93
00:05:57,272 --> 00:06:04,893
un keyn tsuker-ribn, tsu dem hot men nisht getort tsurirn, vayl az me zol geven zen az me nemt a pitsl,

94
00:06:04,917 --> 00:06:06,716
