95
00:06:06,942 --> 00:06:11,593
m'hot, tsu dem, di, di daytshn hobn nit a mol getort, tsu dem rirn.

96
00:06:11,785 --> 00:06:13,433
s'iz gevezn,

97
00:06:13,438 --> 00:06:17,515
