mit di tsuker,

104
00:06:37,770 --> 00:06:41,378
vayl, zogt er, az m'vet im trefn, zogt ⟨er⟩, hengt men im oyf.

105
00:06:43,071 --> 00:06:44,380
s'iz...

106
00:06:43,088 --> 00:06:45,940
dos iz geven a ⟨bonboner⟩, a...?

107
00:06:45,501 --> 00:06:48,966
neyn! gantse zek iz dos gevezn

108
00:06:46,125 --> 00:06:47,620
UNK

109
00:06:48,966 --> 00:06:54,188
mit tsuker., fun d- un dos hot men geshikt avek un fun dem hot men gemakht tsuker.

110
00:06:49,751 --> 00:06:50,751
mit tsuker...

111
00:06:52,082 --> 00:06:54,222
ober dos iz geven far aykh, vayl⟨,⟩

112
