azoy vos tsu dem hot men nisht getort rirn.

116
00:07:01,077 --> 00:07:08,900
un, dort ho'mir zikh geplogt un gemutshet. es iz nisht gevezn dort arbet, hot men undz geyogt aroys

117
00:07:08,900 --> 00:07:10,419
oyf di gas

118
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:14,536
in di k- in, in regn, in di kelt, in di shneyen.

119
00:07:15,201 --> 00:07:20,173
ir zent geven in, in groyse gebeyde mit, mit, mit, mit, mit, mit,

120
00:07:20,213 --> 00:07:21,590
mit betn?

121
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:23,109
betn,

122
00:07:23,132 --> 00:07:32,103
betn ho'mir gehat, ze'mir, dort ze'mir shoyn a bisl veyniker gevezn. in Oyshvits ze'mir geven fertsn mentshn in eyn...

123
00:07:32,177 --> 00:07:34,128
un in... yo.

124
00:07:32,194 --> 00:07:35,917
un do ze'mir a bisl veyniker gevezn UNK

125
00:07:34,928 --> 00:07:37,976
UNK BAD KU⟨VA un⟩ GRÄBEN, di zelbe zakh?

126
00:07:37,408 --> 00:07:40,710
 GRÄBEN, iz geven beser.

127
00:07:39,940 --> 00:07:41,660
a beser...

128
00:07:40,710 --> 00:07:46,703
dort iz geven beser. dort ho'mir shoyn, dort ho'mir gehat nisht aza sakh ire, ze'mir geshlofn,

129
00:07:45,255 --> 00:07:46,211
yo.

130
00:07:46,703 --> 00:07:50,042
ze'mir nisht tsu fil mentshn geven in eyn tsimer.

131
00:07:50,098 --> 00:07:53,500
dort iz a bisl... ober s'hot zeyer veynik gehaltn.

132
00:07:53,372 --> 00:07:55,260
ober ile mol, ale m-

133
00:07:55,380 --> 00:07:57,686
