134
00:07:56,865 --> 00:07:59,711
alts ze'mir undz tsuzamen gevezn.

135
00:07:58,310 --> 00:08:01,888
yo. vi lang zent ir geven in BAD KU⟨V⟩DOVA?

136
00:08:02,502 --> 00:08:07,778
BAD KUDOWA ze'mir gevezn biz v- m'hot undz nisht gefirt

137
00:08:07,918 --> 00:08:16,730
oyf, vi azoy? nu, vi azoy heyst dos? nor,

138
00:08:17,942 --> 00:08:19,927
m'hot aykh gefirt fun

139
00:08:20,206 --> 00:08:21,680
oyf...

140
00:08:20,457 --> 00:08:22,982
BAD KUDOVA biz vanen?

141
00:08:26,042 --> 00:08:27,858
vi azoy heyst dos?

142
00:08:28,017 --> 00:08:31,993
dos iz geven, ir hot gemar⟨ts⟩irt, ir hot gegangen tsu fus?

143
00:08:28,742 --> 00:08:32,645
vu ikh b- vu ikh bin bafrayt gevorn. yo.

144
00:08:32,404 --> 00:08:34,020
ir ⟨gezangen⟩...

145
00:08:32,645 --> 00:08:35,570
vu ze'mir bafrayt gevorn, in...

146
00:08:34,142 --> 00:08:38,118
dos iz a, dos iz geven, vi me ruft es, a ⟨tOtn-MARCH⟩,

147
00:08:39,102 --> 00:08:41,070
vayl a sakh mentshn zenen...

148
00:08:43,060 --> 00:08:46,520
 v⟨u z- z-⟩...

149
00:08:46,107 --> 00:08:47,046
dos i-...

150
00:08:47,372 --> 00:08:51,880
, vu bin ikh bafrayt gevorn? in...

151
00:08:52,131 --> 00:08:56,709
BERGEN-BELSEN? yo. UNK, ober ir zent gegangen tsu fus

152
00:08:52,806 --> 00:08:54,520
BERGEN-BELSEN.

153
00:08:56,709 --> 00:08:59,279
fun BAD KUDOVA...?

154
00:08:56,884 --> 00:08:58,290
tsu fus.

155
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:01,339
tsu fus hot men undz geyogt,

156
00:09:00,805 --> 00:09:01,575
yo.

157
00:09:01,429 --> 00:09:02,840
tog un nakht.

158
00:09:01,648 --> 00:09:03,780
vi lang hot dos genem⟨t⟩?

159
00:09:04,175 --> 00:09:05,480
a por tog.

160
00:09:05,260 --> 00:09:06,469
a por t⟨e⟩g.

161
00:09:06,313 --> 00:09:07,590
a por teg.

162
00:09:06,610 --> 00:09:09,979
vu f- ir flegt shlofn vu? oyfn, oyfn feld?

163
00:09:08,787 --> 00:09:11,050
oyf di shteyner ho'mir,

164
00:09:10,018 --> 00:09:11,429
oyf di shteyner?

165
00:09:11,050 --> 00:09:17,465
oyf di shteyner ze'mir ⟨undz⟩ geshlofn, o⟨ber v-⟩ ven me lozt undz. m'hot ober nisht gelozt shlofn oykh nisht.

166
00:09:11,723 --> 00:09:12,932
oyf di veg?

167
00:09:17,465 --> 00:09:22,090
nor a, a bisl dort, a halbe sho, a sho zikh opruen, un vayter.

168
00:09:22,928 --> 00:09:24,150
un dos iz g-...

169
00:09:22,962 --> 00:09:25,946
un z- un ze'mir ahin ongekumen.

170
00:09:25,946 --> 00:09:31,039
dos iz oykhet gevezn, in shney un in vaser ze'mir gevezn,

171
