shoyn take in BERGEN-BEL⟨ts⟩.

172
00:09:34,065 --> 00:09:37,760
az ze'mir ongekumen, m'hot undz geyogt tsu di arbet,

173
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:45,400
un az ze'mir geblibn shteyn oyf eyn fus, ⟨iz ho'mir im,⟩ gekent shteyn azoy a gantse nakht oyf eyn fus;

174
