un s'iz say vi nor ongetrogn gevezn shney un vaser; in dem iz men gezesn.

176
00:09:53,809 --> 00:09:55,642
velkhe KHODESH iz dos geven?

177
00:09:55,950 --> 00:09:58,038
s- sof may?

178
00:09:58,315 --> 00:10:01,910
dos iz gevezn... nu, far, f-

179
00:09:58,467 --> 00:09:59,830
s'iz nokh...

180
00:10:00,520 --> 00:10:02,270
f- far friling?

181
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:06,950
