bafrayt gevorn, a, zeyer a sakh tsayt

186
00:10:19,025 --> 00:10:23,910
hot men undz shoyn bikhlal nisht gegebn keyn esn. keyn vaser un keyn esn,

187
00:10:23,910 --> 00:10:29,450
