vi lang ze'mir nisht gekumen aheym, un demolts hot es in gantsn oyf mir...

199
00:11:02,912 --> 00:11:04,360
ven hot,

200
00:11:04,380 --> 00:11:07,951
ven hot ongefangen di tsores mitn, mitn, mitn rukn?

201
00:11:07,401 --> 00:11:10,567
mitn rukn hot mir ongehoybn shoyn

